<b>HI ! All Dear CIPHER customer,</b><br>
Welcome to your good support to CIPHER’s product for such a long time.<br>
We set up the basic principle in this RMA policy demonstrating it transparent and clearly.<br>
You can take advantage of the RMA system more friendly and more easily.<br> <br>

I. RMA<br>
˙Definition:<br>
RMA：RETURN MATERIAL AUTHORIZATION.<br>
An approval procedures for customer’s return goods or / return for services.<br><br>

˙Scope of operation:<br>
1. Applicable to the power supply returned for CIPHER”s service, excluding replacing goods. <br>
2. Excluding any item without CIPHER’s acknowledgement in written, nor any Notice of Engineering Changes without a former understanding.<br>
3. Not applicable to any change in Functions, electricity, structure, appearance, reliability or compatibility of product by customer themselves..<br>
4. Not applicable to product of improper compatibility or reliability.<br><br>

˙Confirmation of Guarantee<br>
* Three years of Guarantee period beginning from the delivery date on label or by BARCODE of the product, any special footnote in quotation or purchase order are excluded.<br>
* Guarantee period of service<br>
1 Applicable to keep the original guarantee period, if product after our service within the original guarantee period and more than six months.<br>
2 if product after our service within the original guarantee period and less than six months. Guarantee shall be valid up to six months of replacing parts in the exceeding portion. <br>
3 if returned product exceeding original guarantee period of service. Guarantee shall be valid up to six months of replacing parts only.<br>
* Declaration of exclusions in Guarantee<br>
1. Product information such as : label, BARCODE, MODEL are Lost or broken, unable to be identified<br>
2. Repair or removal of any part of power supply not by CIPHER’s service.<br>
3. Some factor not in product&nbsp; itself, such as: by an external connection, or in an extra ordinary environment.<br>
4. Not conforming to CIPHER recommended peripheral specifications.<br>
5. Counterfeit or fake.<br><br>

II、How to apply for a RMA<br>
1. To apply for RMA, you can find any service point near to yoy among Eastern USA,West USA, Canada, Mainland China , Germany, as well as Taiwan General Office.<br>
2. Please fill the membership information in detail so as to your goods returning or changing more smoothly. You are surely able to Update Information ”by using the web network, to keep your updated data, CIPHER guarantee it will never be released out, nor to use them for any non-related purposes.<br>
3. Please use the formulated requisition form download in web net, your own designed form would not be acceptable otherwise.<br>
4. System will provide you serial No. automatically when you apply. You can also check the status of RMA proogress in returning or changing goods, CIPHER service point will follow your requirements and keep contact with you all the time.<br>
5. Please free to contact with distribution point or sales or mail us if you are unable to select a favorable service point in your area or to fine an answer from any other questions.<br><br>

III、Basic principle of charge <br>
1. Freight : Freight are excluded from Service quotation <br>
l In Guarantee period, Customer pay Freight for delivery product to CIPHER Service Center, while CIPHER pay returned freight for the product after his service. <br>
l Out of Guarantee period, customer pay freight of both product delivery to and return back.<br>
2. Service Charge<br>
l System will provide prelinimary quotation depending on your requirements of service, and will contact you if there is any change of it, Services shall be begun to your approval.<br>
l CIPHER provide services free of charge within the Guarantee period.<br>
l CIPHER will charge for the cost of components and operational expense.<br>
l Service Center repack the returned goods after a standard testing procedures and send it back, Customer will bear theTest fee etc. <br>
l Service Center evaluate the situation and provide estimates according to the damage of returned product because of natural / man made disaster or refit by themselves. <br><br>

IV、Time-limit for services of goods <br>
l Fifteen (15) working days is the time limit in completion of service and return back the customer.<br>
l Service Center will send special notice and contact with customer under any special or unexpected conditions.<br><br>

V.、Result of RMA process<br>
1. Handling Report shall be prepared in completion of each RMA service, You can review any one of your former RMA History Record from our web site.<br>
2. All returned goods after service shall be delivered by cargo transport.<br><br>

VI.、Notice to the RMA<br>
System in need of your entry of BAR CODE No., Model No. …when you are applying a RMA requesition. Please check if all of your product information is complete and tact your local distributor in case of short any information.<br>
1. Please fill in the cause of failure at your best in a RMA requisition. System will provide you preliminary quotation, Service Center can contact your goodness if there is any correction. Service shall only be proceeding according to your agreement of quotation. <br>
2. Please check a complete set of your returned commondity and external package as well, so as to be sure of a safe delivery.<br>
3. Please read the RMA articles before using the system, CIPHER wll send you articles for your approval in receipt of your RMA. <br>
You are in full informed if there is any modification / revision or all of sudden.<br>

